> with a new edutainment video automatically downloaded each month for your lobby and for streaming on your site.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Need to consult with a client on an ongoing case but can\'t meet face to face?</strong>  Your clients will appreciate that they can download our<strong> <a href=\"https://vets-central.com/index.php/a-homepage-section/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"23\">free app</a></strong> to make appointments and utilize the Televet capability for consultations with you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":19}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\" style=\"font-size:19px\">Vets Central is the platform you need to take your practice to the next level! </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\"><!-- wp:button {\"backgroundColor\":\"vivid-red\",\"textColor\":\"white\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-white-color has-vivid-red-background-color has-text-color has-background\" href=\"https://app.vets-central.com\">SIGN UP NOW</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":247,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://vets-central.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/image.dogcat.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-247\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Home','','publish','closed','closed','','home','','','2020-08-18 03:07:20','2020-08-18 03:07:20','',0,'https://vets-central.com/?page_id=19',0,'page','',0),(20,1,'2020-08-14 00:47:33','2020-08-14 00:47:33','<!-- wp:image {\"align